title: #92Noon! Vikings are 1-5?
description: Tons of talkers and calls throughout the show in relation to the Vikings entering bye week with a 1-5 record. Matt Birk, Dave Sinykin join at the end of the first hour, Pete Bercich in the mix for most of the 2nd hour, and Lavelle joins during the final stretch on the passing of Sid Hartman. The show wraps with Gophers HC PJ Fleck!
